 QSSUpdateDate, QSSVersion, Outcome, Version, ReportAs, InternalComment, ApprovedDate, AutoManualFlag, QSSReleasedID 
 from #tmpUpdatedResults  
 
  

 --     --For DXI800 instrument order 
